ZH: 1. 明天就是新年了。
EN: 1. Tomorrow is New Year's Day.

ZH: 2. 我们家每年都有新年聚会。
EN: 2. My family has a New Year's party every year.

ZH: 3. 祝你新年快乐！
EN: 3. Happy New Year to you!

ZH: 4. 新年是我最喜欢的节日之一。
EN: 4. New Year is one of my favorite holidays.

ZH: 5. 我们新年要去旅行。
EN: 5. We are going to travel for New Year.

ZH: 6. 我的新年愿望是健康和幸福。
EN: 6. My New Year's wish is health and happiness.

ZH: 7. 每年新年都是一个新的开始。
EN: 7. Every New Year is a new beginning.

ZH: 8. 我特别喜欢新年的烟火表演。
EN: 8. I especially love the fireworks show on New Year.

ZH: 9. 新年快到了，我要给家人准备礼物。
EN: 9. New Year is coming, I need to prepare gifts for my family.

ZH: 10. 新年是一个全家团聚的时刻。
EN: 10. New Year is a time for family reunion.

ZH: 11. 他们在新年的时候举办了一场盛大的庆祝活动。
EN: 11. They held a grand celebration during New Year.

ZH: 12. 新年的氛围让人充满了希望和期待。
EN: 12. The atmosphere of New Year fills people with hope and expectation.

ZH: 13. 在新年之际，我们祝福所有人都能健康快乐。
EN: 13. On the occasion of New Year, we wish everyone health and happiness.

ZH: 14. 新年的钟声即将敲响。
EN: 14. The bells of New Year are about to ring.

ZH: 15. 新年的第一天我们通常要吃团圆饭。
EN: 15. On the first day of New Year, we usually have a reunion dinner.

ZH: 16. 在新年，我们要给长辈拜年。
EN: 16. During New Year, we pay New Year's visits to our elders.

ZH: 17. 新年是中国最重要的节日之一。
EN: 17. New Year is one of the most important festivals in China.

ZH: 18. 新年的气氛充满了喜庆和欢乐。
EN: 18. The atmosphere of New Year is filled with joy and celebration.

ZH: 19. 在新年之际，人们会穿着传统的节日服装。
EN: 19. On the occasion of New Year, people dress in traditional holiday costumes.

ZH: 20. 我们将在新年里制定新的计划和目标。
EN: 20. We will set new plans and goals in the New Year.
